channel.title: What's your thoughts?
channel.description:
[center]Hey I'm Josh a front-end developer,
looking for something to put my time and effort into in the weekends and evening's.
I've been looking into designing an on-line private RS server for players to enjoy but this isn't really in my interest.
Why I'm here today is because I was just wondering if anyone had any ideas or thoughts on what I should do.
Thanks, Regards Josh[/center]
